title: Casio Men's 'G Shock' Quartz Stainless Steel and Resin Casual Watch, Color:Black (Model: GST-S110-1ACR)
feature: Tough solar powered, shock resistant, 200-meter water resistance, neobrite, double led light, world time, stopwatch, countdown timer, 5 daily alarms
Hourly time signal, hand shift feature, battery level indicator, power saving, full auto-calendar (to year 2099), 12/24-hour format, button operation tone on/off
Water resistant 200m (660ft): in general, suitable for professional marine activity and serious surface water sports, but not diving
description: Wear this men's Casio G-Shock G-Steel watch to embrace a new layer of toughness. Featuring a resin band and stainless steel bezel, this timepiece sports a rugged look and maintains the shock resistant structure that G-Shock is known for.​
